properties.Name: TaskStatusType
properties.Description:
A status that may be applied to a task.

Ex:
- Unscheduled
- Issued for third-party bids
- Planned
- Scheduled
- In Process
- Completed
- Late
- Closed
- Cancelled
- Needs Action
- Unknown
